    <h1> ₊✩ Educaté and Change Newsletter ✩₊</h1>
    <h4>by Arely Ordonez-Chavez</h4>
    <img src="project1.jpg" width="500" />
    <p>This project was assigned in one my sociology courses where we chose an
      existing social issue that we were passionate about and were asked to create a 
      psuedo newsletter in order to share the information we've gradually accumulated 
      throughout the class. In my project, I chose to write about the struggles and 
      under-representation for undocumented students and Latino communities. The purpose 
      of my newsletter was to bring awareness to the lack of resources and attention for 
      these students in order to reform the existing systems that marginalize and penalize 
      these students, and to begin thinking about what programs and services we could 
      implement in schools that can help these students succeed.</p>

    <br/>
    <br/>
