    <h1>•｡ꪆৎ Interview Paper Assignmnet ꪆৎ ˚⋅</h1>
    <h4>by Arely Ordonez-Chavez</h4>
    <img src="ss1.jpg" width="500" />
    <p>In this project I conducted a psuedo research project where I interviewed my father
      to compare Latino immigrants'experience in navigating, raising and maintaining a 
      family in a foriegn country (and the implications it has on mental health and a 
      person's overall health). The purpose of this project was to understand the perceptions 
      immigrants hold about American society and to examine the transformation of the ideals 
      this group holds and how they're challenged. </p>

